text: Sergej Pfeifer (born 20 February 1977) is a German gymnast. He competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dushanbe
